data.description: Motivated Seller! Beautiful 5 Bedroom Bi-level Home over 3500 sqft of living space! . Located just a walk away from Downtown Romulus, minutes from airport and 94/275 expressway.  This well kept home offers oversize Owner Suite w/study, 4 additional bedrooms, 3 full bath, large Great room and Entertainment Room for large gatherings! All appliances included. 2 1/2 car garage w/bonus storage! Don't miss this one it want last long!
